data.description: Welcome to your DREAM HOME in Belton, TX! This charming home, built in 1999, is the perfect place to call your own. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this spacious abode offers ample room for all your needs. The well-maintained property boasts a beautiful backyard and Sideyard, ideal for relaxing or entertaining guests. All of the beautiful trees make for plenty of shade from that Texas sun, and a truly relaxing property.
